  <entry>
    <title>Hexo搭建</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/10/01/Hexo/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/10/01/Hexo/</id>
    <published>2019-10-01T06:54:26.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-10-04T19:08:24.857Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="使用Hexo及Github来建立个人博客"><a href="#使用Hexo及Github来建立个人博客" class="headerlink" title="使用Hexo及Github来建立个人博客"></a>使用Hexo及Github来建立个人博客</h2><h3 id="安装Nodejs"><a href="#安装Nodejs" class="headerlink" title="安装Nodejs"></a>安装Nodejs</h3><p>安装Nodejs使用Npm工具<br>参考资料：(<strong><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://nodejs.org/en/</a></strong>)<br>查看npm版本</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装cnpm"><a href="#安装cnpm" class="headerlink" title="安装cnpm"></a>安装cnpm</h3><p>由于国内网络环境因素，所以安装cnpm<br>下载安装hexo<br>参考资料：(<strong><a href="http://npm.taobao.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://npm.taobao.org/</a></strong>)</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h3 id="Hexo使用"><a href="#Hexo使用" class="headerlink" title="Hexo使用"></a>Hexo使用</h3><h4 id="初始化"><a href="#初始化" class="headerlink" title="初始化"></a>初始化</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>会生成一堆文件</p><hr><h4 id="创建"><a href="#创建" class="headerlink" title="创建"></a>创建</h4><p>参考资料：(<strong><a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html</a></strong>)</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">"My New Post"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h4 id="清理Hexo"><a href="#清理Hexo" class="headerlink" title="清理Hexo"></a>清理Hexo</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h4 id="重新生成静态文件"><a href="#重新生成静态文件" class="headerlink" title="重新生成静态文件"></a>重新生成静态文件</h4><p>参考资料：(<strong><a href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html</a></strong>)</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h3 id="Run-server"><a href="#Run-server" class="headerlink" title="Run server"></a>Run server</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h4 id="启动hexo"><a href="#启动hexo" class="headerlink" title="启动hexo"></a>启动hexo</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h4 id="部署远端"><a href="#部署远端" class="headerlink" title="部署远端"></a>部署远端</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h3 id="下载更改主题"><a href="#下载更改主题" class="headerlink" title="下载更改主题"></a>下载更改主题</h3><p>下载主题<br>从GitHub上下载了一个主题放到本地目录</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/MOxFIVE/hexo-theme-yelee.git &quot;/Blog/themes/yelee&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改默认主题landscape为yelee<br>修改_config.yml文件中配置</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Extensions</span><br><span class="line">## Plugins: https://hexo.io/plugins/</span><br><span class="line">## Themes: https://hexo.io/themes/</span><br><span class="line">theme: (landscape) yelee</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="部署GitHub"><a href="#部署GitHub" class="headerlink" title="部署GitHub"></a>部署GitHub</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git </span><br><span class="line">  repo: git@github.com:&#123;GitHub用户名&#125;/&#123;GitHub用户名&#125;.github.io.git </span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
